{"tid":261224,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家食過最好食及難食的醫院飯","createTime":"2017-05-28T09:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T16:16:06.000Z","uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5165df6f0f3292c590fbeeacd7dcf3ce7b58511","tid":261224,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:38:54.000Z","msg":"我講的是病人飯<br />\n唔係canteen<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解有的人講到醫院飯狗都唔食咁<br />\n<br />\n可能屋企本身煮食都偏少少淡味<br />\n我食醫院飯覺得食得落口而且好enjoy<br />\n<br />\n細個成日入某醫院，我都唔記得左點解有次阿婆可以幫我R到一碗叉燒飯<br />\n明明果次我應該要食粥...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5602261f0191d278fc70cfb6f20691bdeb70dd58","tid":261224,"uid":192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T10:48:05.000Z","msg":"開呢d post想人有應都幾難"},{"pid":"edc81500f09e44f01450d5992795f811b4f933ba","tid":261224,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:48:03.000Z","msg":"只住過QE<br />\n午餐啲餸好似烚出嚟咁<br />\n不過當時覺得好餓, 係咁食..."},{"pid":"db74bf6621b2a47a023b5d70cae85b5a49c42124","tid":261224,"uid":76845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:59:35.000Z","msg":"煮過港安<br />\n好好食"},{"pid":"fe449833c87e5603a7f873b82d2f4ee37531a93e","tid":261224,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T16:09:10.000Z","msg":"QE好難食<br />\n法國好食好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b12d501ac6b3edcf2ef6758d82fb6b35d041308","tid":261224,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T16:09:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>煮過港安<br />\n好好食</blockquote><br />\n荃灣定半山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 私家一定好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a151c183518375ba377caba70099b401f9d0866b","tid":261224,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T16:10:23.000Z","msg":"醫院不嬲要少油鹽糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 煮到透先出"},{"pid":"1645678c01f5bc6f25785374644bccd134bffb71","tid":261224,"uid":47529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T16:16:46.000Z","msg":"威爾斯 次次都係入佢<br />\n最難食既係碗粟米粥 真係好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我每次都會食曬<br />\n因為大部份時候一入到去就NPO冇得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得病人食個啲應該冇話邊間醫院特別難食<br />\n我估去到最極端咪又係粥"},{"pid":"ad3d700631927b44b0fda89e990b70c81dabb3bb","tid":261224,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T16:20:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>QE好難食<br />\n法國好食好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我住法國 食過梅菜蒸鯇魚<br />\n唔差 不過等左成個鐘先送到病房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bead57556d0a786cb8557a3f432d99455133fff6","tid":261224,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T10:24:56.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"ad29c1959ee91c8cdb0443b80129293530739769","tid":261224,"uid":40997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"那打素 既油脾同沙薑脾唔差 仲有奶油南瓜雞柳都ok <br />\n羅漢齋最垃圾"},{"pid":"7bdf13684578aa7499220f0822eed0dd5ce1de27","tid":261224,"uid":77632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T14:09:57.000Z","msg":"伊院<br />\n朝早個粥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好食係個包同鈣思寶&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"88fda451490dc1c2f0856d71a51e4709b378c60b","tid":261224,"uid":17313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T14:24:00.000Z","msg":"每次一吊水就無得食野<br />\n吊完可以食番野 你就會覺得個飯係全世界最好食既飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af951b1cc5ac709a1f57502316b41f862c36fa5","tid":261224,"uid":34714,"like":0,"